  "text": "Cells were lysed in TNES buffer [50 mM TrisHCl (pH 7.5), 2 mM EDTA, 100 mM NaCl, 1 mM sodium orthovanadate, and 1% NP40 containing protease inhibitors (20 µg/mL aprotinin, 20 µg/mL leupeptin, and 1 mM phenylmethylsulfonyl fluoride)]. The detection of HIF-1α was as described previously [CITATION_1] .",
